"**Armor Class** 17 (natural armor)    \n"
"**Hit Points** 157 (15d10 + 75)    \n"
"**Speed** 40 ft. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/glabrezu.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| STR      | DEX     | CON      | INT     | WIS     | CHA     |\n"
"|----------|---------|----------|---------|---------|---------|\n"
"| 20 (+5) | 15 (+2) | 21 (+5) | 19 (+4) | 17 (+3) | 16 (+3) |   \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/glabrezu.md:23
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Saving Throws** Str +9, Con +9, Wis +7, Cha +7    \n"
"**Damage Resistances** cold, fire, lightning; bludgeoning, piercing, and "
"slashing from nonmagical attacks    \n"
"**Damage Immunities** poison    \n"
"**Condition Immunities** poisoned    \n"
"**Senses** truesight 120 ft., passive Perception 13    \n"
"**Languages** Abyssal, telepathy 120 ft.    \n"
"**Challenge** 9 (5,000 XP)    \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/glabrezu.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Innate Spellcasting.** The glabrezu's spellcasting ability is Intelligence "
"(spell save DC 16). The glabrezu can innately cast the following spells, "
"requiring no material components:    \n"
"At will: **_darkness_**, **_detect magic_**, **_dispel magic_**    \n"
"1/day each: **_confusion_**, **_fly_**, **_power word stun_**    \n"
"**Magic Resistance.** The glabrezu has advantage on saving throws against "
"spells and other magical effects. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/glabrezu.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Multiattack.** The glabrezu makes four attacks: two with its pincers and "
"two with its fists. Alternatively, it makes two attacks with its pincers and "
"casts one spell.    \n"
"**Pincer.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +9 to hit, reach 10 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 16 (2d10 + 5) bludgeoning damage. If the target is a Medium "
"or smaller creature, it is grappled (escape DC 15). The glabrezu has two "
"pincers, each of which can grapple only one target.    \n"
"**Fist.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +9 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"7 (2d4 + 2) bludgeoning damage.\n"
msgstr ""
